{
  "texts": [
    "Section 3 is dedicated to the fundamentals of soft topology, its foundational literature, and its relationship with topology.",
    "Other topics in soft set theory are overviewed in Sect. 4.",
    "These subjects include: other mathematical structures with a soft-set-based approach, data filling of incomplete soft sets, parameter reduction of soft sets and fuzzy soft sets, aggregation, plus an outline of soft probability.",
    "Section 5 is dedicated to decision-making.",
    "Section 6 concludes our survey and identifies potential areas for future research."
  ]
}